title: Ep. -  199 - BEHIND THE SCENES OF THE OSBOURNES AND NEWLYWEDS: NICK AND JESSICA
description:
Sue Kolisky is a comedian, writer, and producer of several reality television hit shows including The Osbournes and Newlyweds: Nick and Jessica on MTV, and Top Chef on Bravo. She gives a behind the scenes look at how the shows were made and what made them unique and iconic. 


My freshman college roommate Shannon reviews this week’s episode of Below Deck on Bravo. 


Reality Life with Kate Casey
